<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Instagram Followers Shop</title>
<style>
body {
  text-align: center;
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f8f8f8;
  color: #333;
}
h1 {
  color: #E1306C; /* Instagram pink */
  margin-top: 30px;
}
h2 {
  margin-top: 20px;
}
.package {
  border: 2px solid #E1306C;
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 15px 25px;
  margin: 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background-color: #fff;
}
button {
  background-color: #E1306C;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  padding: 15px 30px;
  font-size: 16px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-top: 15px;
}
button:hover {
  background-color: #c1275b;
}
img.qr {
  margin-top: 15px;
  width: 150px;
  height: 150px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>Instagram Followers Shop</h1>
<p>Yaha Instagram followers aur likes milte hai</p>

<h2>Packages</h2>
<div class="package">1000 Followers - ₹50</div>
<div class="package">5000 Followers - ₹200</div>
<div class="package">10000 Followers - ₹350</div>

<h2>Order Now</h2>
<p>QR code scan kare ya button se WhatsApp khol kar order kare:</p>
<img class="qr" src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://wa.me/your_number_here" alt="WhatsApp QR Code">

<br>
<button onclick="window.location.href='https://wa.me/your_number_here';">
Order Now via WhatsApp
</button>

</body
